node.text: When @themensgroomer told me about Angela and Joshua, I knew this was a story I had to witness first hand and I’m so glad I did. The ultimate purpose and happiness comes through service. Hope you enjoy. Also a big thanks to the boys @joestaehly @_rozes @mattpiegari for capturing & believing in this amazing project. Much love and peace!

node.title: The simplest acts of kindness can change a life forever.

node.text: So many incredible things about this movie - one being it was the first movie back to shoot in Los Angeles during quarantine. Very much in an unknown territory and paving the way for production safety protocols. It was strange at times - especially while shooting a movie about the pandemic. Can’t wait for you guys to see!

node.text:
Such a pleasure to be a part of the @CarolinaHerrera family in their new fragrance campaign for “212 Heroes”. We wanted to celebrate the spirit of feeling Forever Young, forever liberated of rules and being able to express ourselves to the fullest in whatever it is that we love. Such a fun shoot! Thanks to everyone involved. 
#212ForeverYoung #212CarolinaHerrera
